WHERE IT IS APPLIED
On-camera AI-ISP (Snapdragon Spectra, Apple Neural Engine),
cloud-based image restoration, generative fill in editing
software, automated dailies color grading, deepfake detection
and content authentication, JPEG AI compression, and AI-driven
